{
  "texts": [
    "First, due to the limited amount of datasets and previous literature on minority groups and additional backgrounds, our study was only able to consider the binary gender when analyzing biases.",
    "We do stress, however, the importance of further extending our study to fairness issues for other gender minority groups as future works.",
    "In addition, our study primarily focuses on reference letters to narrow the scope of analysis.",
    "We recognize that there's a large space of professional documents now possible due to the emergence of LLMs, such as resumes, peer evaluations, and so on, and encourage future researchers to explore fairness issues in other categories of professional documents.",
    "Additionally, due to cost and compute constraints, we were only able to experiment with the ChatGPT API and 3 other open-source LLMs."
  ]
}